# float-loop

Hot path: FloatV boxing, env lookup, while-loop overhead — the Double twin of
`arith-loop`. Exercises the `dcell` unboxed-double lane (`var x: Double` loop
vars + float arith/compare) vs the boxed `cell`/`Emit.arith` path.

```scalascript
def workload(): Double =
  var i: Double = 0.0
  var sum: Double = 0.0
  while i < 1000000.0 do
    sum = sum + i
    i = i + 1.0
  sum
```
